38337af34547f14c","tid":522890,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a94536a39db02044ce4e1aaeafe7a1f759b92d","tid":522890,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"好多新會然<br />\n樓主同劉細良既過節都唔知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"單戀無罪巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"我成日都唔知A level考3個A黎做甚麼<br />\n我又唔係話想拿獎學金<br />\n阿媽係教畜都可以負擔我大學學費<br />\n但係無啦啦考3個A就得罪有錢仔皇仁1993-94年總領袖生徐紹基(但我班皇仁同學話我提住徐生係總領袖生係我不對)<br />\n佢就吩咐佢女友害我<br />\n跟住又扮晒話係&quot;separate entity&quot;<br />\n佢女友的事唔關佢事<br />\n佢女友就賴話成篇偽造訪問都係佢個會考狀元老細寫(雖然我就唔係好信)<br />\n而劉細良於2014年在花生台就解釋話自己只係寫了標題《狀元考試考上癮》七個字，其他與佢無關<br />\n所以我而家覺得係報應，報應我呢d日日在學校俾人打的低賤人無啦啦拿3A再拿獎學金<br />\n做賤人入到大學都偷笑，點解要多徐紹基一個A(雖然佢去LSE讀書，我多過佢一個A都搶唔到佢份獎學金，因為我拿的獎學金只供香港升讀大學之用，出國就無份)<br />\n但徐紹基就係上等人<br />\n我呢d賤人考試得好成績就實係因此考試考上癮，返工覺得好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4943db8eb0238f2f1cac51d23fc9ff99c73b1257","tid":522890,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5843893cee8cce1639b4c0e00a6c0ee1759bc8e1","tid":522890,"uid":103347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0277726324a47bbf01634ea3e6fa11f348fee5d","tid":522890,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba3d0422e6cccc35f9901c038337af34547f14c","tid":522890,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ado